tinker

Class Tinker_Parser

  • java.lang.Object
    • tinker.Tinker_Parser

  • public abstract class Tinker_Parser
extends java.lang.Object
    A class for defining the structure of Tinker formatted files. Tinker is a MD software created by Jay Ponder Lab, Department of Chemistry, at Washington University, Saint Louis, Missouri. Information about Tinker can be found here.
    Author:
    Trevor Fisher
    See Also:
    BulkSystem

        Parameters:

        system - The BulkSystem to read the atoms from the file into.
